$ 到 $B C ， C D$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\r\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2324},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3169,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\r\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3666}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"159mvg6","at":1773364404305},"key":"01零散资料/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】3.0.md"},"smart_blocks:01零散资料/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】3.0.md#目录": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05575132,-0.01065719,0.0816032,0.03271078,0.03642074,-0.00932606,-0.05825154,0.0423848,0.03917409,0.05866653,0.03840018,-0.07375424,0.03904824,-0.00012087,0.01298439,-0.0009393,-0.01559457,-0.02587581,-0.05874792,-0.01531047,0.12950817,-0.01005283,-0.00990202,-0.05040916,0.05625389,0.06379931,-0.0114507,-0.08128455,-0.03292644,-0.19470821,-0.0041618,0.08655699,0.07567733,0.0246086,0.03851275,-0.06375502,-0.0197576,0.08461753,-0.00137355,0.0538221,0.00483774,0.0766177,0.01815061,0.01265555,-0.01385465,-0.08031847,-0.06818453,-0.01228934,0.03647123,-0.01922248,-0.03590541,-0.01499663,0.01058774,0.03515919,-0.02640485,0.00648003,0.04220396,-0.00424943,0.03563147,0.03362874,0.01788311,-0.00553005,-0.22232226,0.03389438,0.05431787,-0.01554576,-0.02516333,-0.05419446,0.01126019,0.06684167,-0.02026872,0.00212194,0.00728726,0.00229543,-0.02259539,-0.03842948,-0.00919351,-0.08518051,-0.03816798,-0.04887083,-0.0406439,0.09081778,-0.06496163,0.01003592,-0.01234223,0.06050729,0.00790713,-0.06104501,0.00016975,-0.0043559,-0.0033863,-0.0102524,-0.03118159,0.02058246,-0.08610892,-0.05709931,0.01425161,0.0089123,-0.00862079,0.